data.description: Welcome to 1376 E Highway 81, McDonough! This stunning property located in the iconic "Lincoln Ranch" offers a perfect blend of comfort and style perfect for multigenerational living. Situated in a desirable location and 14 acres - the main home features 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing ample space for your needs. Plus a full finished basement apartment, complete with a kitchen, bedroom, bathroom, living room and more. The spacious living areas are flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with modern appliances and plenty of storage. There is a separate garage, perfect for that man-cave and plenty of storage! In the rear of the property you will find a complete bardominium with a 3rd living space - full kitchen and living room, bedroom, etc. perfect for the in-laws or additional income from an Air BB or rental. You can use the garage portion for your car collection! Outside, you'll find a beautiful massive yard perfect for pets and kids, even farm life. Bring your horses, chickens, goats! With convenient access to nearby amenities, this home is an absolute gem. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
